data.description: Beckett Ridge Beauty!  Custom built brick home in a lovely golf course community.  New laminate flooring on first and second floors.  Kitchen with granite counter tops, stainless appliances, and a gas cooktop, flows into a charming family room with fire place and wall of windows for pretty view of the private back yard.  Living room with French doors could be first floor study. Second floor has four spacious bedrooms with large closets. Finished lower level has a rec room and study/craft room. First floor laundry and oversized garage. Back yard has a pergola on the deck plus a paver patio with a fire pit, backs up to one of 5 playgrounds in the community and walking path.  Roof 2022, A/C 2023.
